I mean sure if you ignore the fact that there are more races in this game than white women.

{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}} 

Giving a similar playstyle to another race is kinda what you should expect. Because there will be illusion-based champions of Vastayan heritage and people will want an illusion-based Vastayan champion. And here we are.

Yup, just like Karma's shield bomb giving to fucking Ivern's ult.

And they won't give it back to her because they want to cater to "her new players" when all her old players are asking for it back constantly.

